 currently predicted.\nTags: * EIA\n* US\n* gas production\n* gas supply\n* gas prices * gas output\nLatest**\n### Latest\n** * #### QazaqGaz and NCOC bolster alliance with new gas projects in Kazakhstan\n10:25 (UTC+04)EconomyMaterials \n* #### Turkmenistan aiming for stars with its cotton harvest plans for 2025\n10:20 (UTC+04)EconomyMaterials \n* #### Cargo traffic through Iranian airports faces downturn in 4M2025\n10:16 (UTC+04)EconomyMaterials  ...    \n* [#### U.S. gas production growth to slow as prices trend upward\n04:27 (UTC+04)EconomyMaterials  ...    * [#### Uzbekistan’s stock market trading volume soars nine"
